A vintage 1960s propaganda poster style illustration showing a diverse crowd of people connected by flowing ribbons in red, white, and blue tones, rising upward from street level toward a bright sky. The figures progress from crawling silhouettes at the bottom, to walking figures in the middle, to running and finally soaring people with outstretched arms at the top, creating a dynamic diagonal composition. The aesthetic features bold flat colors, halftone dot patterns, and strong geometric shapes reminiscent of mid-century political campaign artwork. Warm golden light bathes the ascending figures while cool shadows anchor those still learning to stand, conveying grassroots momentum and collective empowerment.
